@startuml Admin_MonitoringAnalytics

title Admin - Monitoring & Analytics (Module D)

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "REPORTS" {
    usecase "View System\nStatistics" as MA1
    usecase "View User\nGrowth Report" as MA2
    usecase "View Job\nPosting Report" as MA3
    usecase "View Application\nReport" as MA4
    usecase "View Interview\nStatistics" as MA5
    usecase "Export Report\n(CSV/PDF)" as MA6
}

Admin --> MA1: 1. System stats
Admin --> MA2: 2. User growth
Admin --> MA3: 3. Job postings
Admin --> MA4: 4. Applications
Admin --> MA5: 5. Interviews
MA1 --> MA6: 6. Export
MA2 --> MA6: Export
MA3 --> MA6: Export

note right of MA1
  **Priority:** P2 (Nice-to-have)
  **Status:** Future Phase
end note

@enduml
